tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE QuantumKeysUsagePermissions (
    key_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    key_name TEXT NOT NULL,
    usage_description TEXT,
    creation_date DATE,
    last_usage_date DATE,
    permissions VARCHAR(255)
)

CREATE TABLE KeyUsage (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    key_id INT,
    user_id INT,
    usage_date TIMESTAMP,
    usage_description TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE quantum_keys (
  key_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  key_value VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  expiration_date DATE,
  user_id INT,
  FOREIGN KEY (user_id) REFERENCES quantum_users(user_id)
);

CREATE TABLE key_usage (
  usage_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  key_id INT,
  usage_date TIMESTAMP,
  event_type VARCHAR(50),
  event_description TEXT,
  FOREIGN KEY (key_id) REFERENCES quantum_keys(key_id)
);

CREATE TABLE quantum_keys (
    key_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    key_value VARCHAR(255),
    creation_date TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE key_usage (
    usage_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    key_id INT,
    user_id INT,
    usage_timestamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE key_permissions (
    permission_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    key_id INT,
    user_id INT,
    permission_type VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE key_access_logs (
    log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    key_id INT,
    user_id INT,
    access_timestamp TIMESTAMP
)
